Please see <a class="external-link" href="../../../../downloads/slider/SNPsTable.pdf">SNPs Table</a> for a description of this file.<br /><br /><a class="external-link" href="../../../../downloads/slider/ExpandedTable3.pdf">Expanded Table 3</a> (from the Slider paper) is available which includes extended information on the alignment accuracy of Slider compared to Eland and RMAP.<br /><br /><br />
<h3>Full datasets</h3>
<br />Two larger datasets are included here for Slider testing:<br /><a class="external-link" href="../../../../downloads/slider/T02_full_data.tar.gz">http://www.bcgsc.ca/downloads/slider/T02_full_data.tar.gz</a><br /><a class="external-link" href="../../../../downloads/slider/CT302_full_data.tar.gz">http://www.bcgsc.ca/downloads/slider/CT302_full_data.tar.gz</a><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />



